        <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>Resara is a sobriety tracking application designed to help users monitor and maintain their recovery journey from various addictions. The App provides features including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Sobriety day tracking</li>
            <li>Daily pledge system</li>
            <li>Journal entries</li>
            <li>Milestone celebrations</li>
            <li>Bio-Sync Recovery (HealthKit integration)</li>
            <li>AI-powered recovery coaching (Premium feature)</li>
            <li>Advanced analytics and insights (Premium feature)</li>
            <li>Motivational quotes (Premium feature)</li>
            <li>Smart notifications (Premium feature)</li>
        </ul>

